title: Caro Emerald (Vocal Jazz) - Riviera Life (Dutch Treat ^B060)
description:
Another sweet Dutch girl who makes interesting classy music and deserves some attention. Unfortunately the sound is not what it could and maybe should be. However still good enough to play it publicly anyway.... Enjoy,
